text: FX (Japanese: FX日本) is an Japanese pay television channel owned by Warner Bros. Discovery EMEA. The channel originally launched as the Japanese version of Discovery Home & Health on 1 December 2005. On 6 May 2024, Warner Bros. Discovery EMEA announced that the Japanese version of Discovery Home & Health would be rebranded as FX on 6 August 2024. == Logos == file:Discovery H&H.png;|1 June 2022-6 August 2024 file:FX Logo 2023.svg|6 August 2024-present Category:Television channels in Asia
